FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common queries about our food delivery service
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the food delivery app work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app allows you to browse local restaurants, select your favorite dishes, place an order, and track your delivery in real-time. Simply download the app, create an account, and start ordering!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Delivery fees vary based on your location and the restaurant you're ordering from. The exact fee will be displayed before you confirm your order. We also offer a subscription service for free delivery on eligible orders.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How long does delivery usually take?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Delivery times depend on various factors such as distance, traffic, and restaurant preparation times. On average, most orders are delivered within 30-45 minutes. You can track your order in real-time through the app.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I schedule an order for later?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes! Our app allows you to schedule orders in advance. Simply select the 'Schedule for Later' option during checkout and choose your preferred delivery date and time.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: What if there's an issue with my order?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: If you experience any problems with your order, please use the 'Help' section in the app to report the issue. Our customer support team is available 24/7 to assist you and ensure your satisfaction.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does our food delivery app work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app connects you with local restaurants and delivers food straight to your door. Simply browse menus, place your order, and track your delivery in real-time.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Delivery fees vary based on your location and the restaurant you choose. The exact fee will be displayed before you complete your order. We also offer a subscription service for free delivery on eligible orders.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How long does delivery usually take?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Delivery times typically range from 30-45 minutes, depending on your location, the restaurant's preparation time, and current demand. You can always check the estimated delivery time before placing your order.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Can I schedule an order for later?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes! Our app allows you to schedule orders up to a week in advance. Simply select your desired delivery time during checkout, and we'll make sure your food arrives fresh at the specified time.
